N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode drink it up with Bay Area legends Too $hort, Mistah F.A.B., and Yukmouth of the Luniz. The guys also joined by Benzino talk battling, the Bay Area scene, and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
